version 1.7.0 26 August 2014

  • [New] Custom Header via Theme Options panel
  • [New] Single page team member
  • [New] Homepage widget: team members 3 columns with profile button
  • [New] Homepage widget: team members 4 columns with profile button
  • [New] Page Template: team members 3 columns
  • [New] Page Template: team members 4 columns
  • [Updated] Twitter Bootstrap version 3.2.0
  • [Fixed] Recent Posts Home widget
  • [Fixed] Minor CSS issues
  • [Changed] Theme files structure

version 1.5.5 - 20.06.2014

  • [Update] Font Awesome icons version 4.1.0
  • [Update] Theme Options panel version 2.4.2
  • [Added] Scroll top button
  • [Fixed] Main menu style
  • [Improved] Pick date for articles from WP config

version 1.5.2 - 19.05.2014

  • [NEW] Home Widget: Practice Areas 3 Columns
  • [NEW] Page Template: Practice Areas 3 Columns
  • [Fixed] 3rd level menu for small devices
  • [Updated] Child theme
  • [Updated] functions.php file

version 1.5.0 - 14.04.2014

  • [NEW] Lawyers theme is now compatible with WPML plugin
  • [NEW] Home Recent Articles widget
  • [Added] Google Maps option for contact page template
  • [Added] Custom URL for practice areas item
  • [Updated] Theme Options panel to the latest version 2.3.4
  • [Updated] theme child
  • [Improved] Modal Window practice item
  • [Improved] Main menu
  • [Improved] Testimonials slider control navigation
  • [Fixed] Logo image responsive
  • [Fixed] Responsive images for custom page templates

version 1.0.9 - 01.03.2014

  • [Added] Fax field option in the contact page
  • [Fixed] About page section titles to be hidden when the input field is empty
  • [Fixed] home slider text for smaller screen devices
  • [Updated] .mo and .po files

version 1.0.8 - 26.02.2014

  • [Added] Home Video widget
  • [Added] Option for displaying Practice Area Single Item: via modal window or via normal page
  • [Updated] Theme Options panel to the latest version
  • [Updated] Twitter Bootstrap Framework
  • Minor CSS changes
